  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Bar Association is dissatisfied with the removal of protesters in Calicut",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Bar Association of Sri Lanka has expressed dissatisfaction with the forcible removal of protesters in Calicut.",
        "In a letter to the Inspector General of Police and the Commander, the Sri Lanka Lawyers Association has pointed out that the police and the military have been criticizing the President and the government, criticizing the president and the government.",
        "We continue to remind you that people should be allowed to exercise their freedom of expression, including their freedom of expression, and the Bar Association of Sri Lanka (BASL) has stated that the solution to the current crisis is to restrict the rights of the people to a country where the people are facing a major crisis due to a shortage of fuel and essential commodities.",
        "The Bar Association of Sri Lanka (BASL) has said that the use of force by the armed forces should not be used to quell demonstrations and refusal to act."
      ],
